      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=k48mgf8cmd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=k48mgf8cmd]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=hl5bagqyxm]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hl5bagqyxm]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=jwxvm9krl9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jwxvm9krl9]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"hl5bagqyxm\">Resource</span></strong>: HDRI</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"jwxvm9krl9\">Captured by</span></strong>: Arkell Rasiah, Christophe Hery, and Jean-Claude Kalache.</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"k48mgf8cmd\">Use</span></strong>: Attach this map to a PxrDomeLight</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/piper_hdri/8763_stinson_beach.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064810&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064810&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608436240\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"c9fbf0d2-3287-4f33-a1c1-b82cdfffaa3c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064810&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064810&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"PiperBeach-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>This HDRI collection was captured at Stinson Beach, California, which was the visual inspiration for Pixar's short film <strong>Piper.&nbsp;</strong>This collection was used while developing the look for the film.</p><p>Legend tells of <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loren_Carpenter\" rel=\"nofollow\">Loren Carpenter</a> showing up serendipitously at the beach right as the camera rig broke...and of course he happened to be walking with tools to fix it at the crack of dawn...</p><iframe class=\"youtube-player conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-local-id=\"3884c96e-8fd6-4a6e-869d-11daf6f820b0\" data-macro-id=\"efff5fffe858080b5ac693e2dd742145bb87a9632e35b7568d7cb7dff0ace741\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/_LuQFp1Lrfo?wmode=opaque\" style=\"width: 960px; height: 540px\" type=\"text/html\">\n</iframe>\n    \n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"piper-sand-01-viewport.jpg\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/piper-sand-01-viewport.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284231206&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/piper-sand-01-viewport.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284231206&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"380\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607814065\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"piper-sand-01-viewport.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"d528aa8e-5cd4-49f1-ad8f-489106b09211\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/piper-sand-01-viewport.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284231206&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=792&amp;height=376 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/piper-sand-01-viewport.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284231206&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=188 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"piper-sand-01-render.jpg\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/piper-sand-01-render.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284238207&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/piper-sand-01-render.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284238207&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"380\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607944992\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"piper-sand-01-render.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"2afa22ba-2b9d-43ac-bb0d-a0afbb13f2a3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/piper-sand-01-render.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284238207&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=792&amp;height=376 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/piper-sand-01-render.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758284238207&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=188 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-local-id=\"abc9483f-72d8-425a-9c81-26318306514d\" data-macro-id=\"3987e6865d17dcbc537936721f14e526806258d68c205cb4d3d995a1d96689dd\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/197975265\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"8764_stinson_beach_shaderballs.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/8764_stinson_beach_shaderballs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284331281&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=168\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/8764_stinson_beach_shaderballs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284331281&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"1152\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608010515\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"8764_stinson_beach_shaderballs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"afe06d96-9896-420d-b829-fad339ca731c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/8764_stinson_beach_shaderballs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284331281&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1152&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/8764_stinson_beach_shaderballs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284331281&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=168 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"PiperBeach-How-to\">How-to</h2><p>Drag the contents of the&nbsp;<strong>Materials</strong>&nbsp;folder into your&nbsp;<strong>Asset Library &gt; EnvironmentMaps&nbsp;</strong>folder. The files are organized by category and can be easily searched in your preset browser.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"baaf3b79-47b4-4e4c-80d0-b5429226cb59\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Make sure to transfer the installation&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki.pixar.com/display/RFM22/Preset+Browser+in+Maya\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>RenderManAssetLibrary</strong></a>&nbsp;folder to a location with full writing privileges.</p></div></div><p>Once you transfer the Materials folder and move your Asset Library into a different location, it is important to tell Maya through the preferences that you want to use the new path.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284065201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284065201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"622\" data-width=\"776\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608436249\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"c8f0a159-f471-4595-917b-e3186974aeef\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284065201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=776&amp;height=622 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284065201&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609 1x\" /></span><p>Or you can create a new environment variable in your Maya.env file, which&nbsp;will make sure you are always pointing to the right folder:</p><p><code>RMAN_ASSET_LIBRARY = /My/Folder/Example/RenderManAssetLibrary</code></p><hr /><h3 id=\"PiperBeach-Copyright\">Copyright</h3><p>Stinson Beach HDRI files are licensed under a <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License</a>. You can use and redistribute as long as you credit the original authors.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"by-nc.png\" width=\"179\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284440298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=179&amp;height=62\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284440298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"34\" data-width=\"97\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607814075\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"by-nc.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"4f4c540e-f665-4679-b604-c2e1806cb29f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284440298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=358&amp;height=124 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284440298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=179&amp;height=62 1x\" /></span><p /><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064809&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436225/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064809&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608436237\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436225\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"6fecb029-59a9-4dce-b5e0-d369e425be86\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064809&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436225/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284064809&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
